From e78d3b2a5c60b596caa77ae333ca285486b09fe3 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Konstantin Komarov <almaz.alexandrovich@paragon-software.com>
Date: Thu, 9 Sep 2021 13:15:20 +0300
Subject: [PATCH 80/92] fs/ntfs3: Add sync flag to ntfs_sb_write_run and
 al_update

This allows to wait only when it's requested.
It speeds up creation of hardlinks.

Signed-off-by: Konstantin Komarov <almaz.alexandrovich@paragon-software.com>
---
 fs/ntfs3/attrib.c   | 2 +-
 fs/ntfs3/attrlist.c | 6 +++---
 fs/ntfs3/frecord.c  | 2 +-
 fs/ntfs3/fslog.c    | 8 ++++----
 fs/ntfs3/fsntfs.c   | 8 ++++----
 fs/ntfs3/inode.c    | 2 +-
 fs/ntfs3/ntfs_fs.h  | 4 ++--
 fs/ntfs3/xattr.c    | 2 +-
 8 files changed, 17 insertions(+), 17 deletions(-)

